title: FULLY REMODELED 2022! Single Family Home, 3BR, 2 BA, 2 Car Garage
posting_body: ['You have to see this home!!!', 'It has a Fully Remodeled Kitchen, Bathroom & all Window are BRAND NEW!', 'You are basically moving into a BRAND NEW, energy efficient home!', 'This place is great for everyone in the family.', 'This 1555 square foot townhouse home has 3 legal bedrooms and 2 bathrooms and a 2 Car attached garage.', 'This home is in the Scott County School District and about 12 miles from Shakopee.', 'You are are responsible for your rent, utilities, renters insurance.', 'Pet Policy\t*Cats & *Small Dogs OK *Pet Fee required - $300 per animal, per year.', 'MAKE SURE YOU LEAVE A MESSAGE WHEN CALLING.', 'CALLS ARE ONLY RETURNED IN THE ORDER', 'THE MESSAGE IS TAKEN.', 'There is a $75 Rental Application / Background Check per adult (18+) that takes roughly 5-20 business days to complete so please plan accordingly.', 'The Background check fee is non-refundable.', 'Once received, someone from our staff will contact you for a walk through of the home within 24-48 business hours.', 'If you are in need of another dept, please send us an email with your questions / concerns.', 'PLEASE NOTE:', 'WE DO NOT RETURN ANY CALLS WITHOUT THIS INFORMATION.', 'WE USE THIS INFORMATION TO FORWARD TO THE APPROPRIATE DEPT THAT WILL BE ABLE TO HELP YOU.', '(SHOWINGS, ACCOUNTING, MAINTENANCE)', 'Keywords: Southwest Metro, End Unit, Dual Garage, All one level, inexpensive, luxury, Spacious, clean, New, newly built, Eden Prairie, Prior lake, burnsville, Savage, Burnsville, Jordan, ISD #191, ISD # 196, ISD # 720, Shakopee, Savage, Prior Lake, and the Jackson, Louisville, and Sand Creek Township, Eagan, Burnsville, Apple Valley, Rosemount, Inver Grove Heights, Bloomington, Richfield, NR Enterprises, NREnterprises, NREnterprisesLLC, NR Enterprises LLC, NR Enterprise LLC, NRE, NR Ent, NR E, HRA, Section 8, VA, Temporary housing, Insurance loss, Fire & water damage, short term, month to month lease, farmington dakota scott']
